                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-574727317" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="574727317">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zheng3000/">matthew</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-08-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一旦成功，革命的正当性便结束了。任何政权，念念不忘历史是如何选择了它，当初它是如何赢得了革命，必致灾难。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="658503390">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-658503390" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-658503390" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="658503390">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/darkma/">突尼西亚的卓玛</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-03-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">杨早文章是好看的，但这些零碎短章去写画这么一个大事件就嫌太轻薄，还不如直接写成章回小说咧。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="819697209">
